snippet.title: New Surprise Testimony! Johnny Depp Amber Heard update!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's sister Whitney, her ex boyfriend who was dating her at the time of this incident has decided to come forward!! This is amazing BOMBSHELL information that directly refutes Whitney and Amber's testimony!

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard the complete story part 2 - https://youtu.be/JsMEJhMjTGA

Bombshell News! The ACLU planned all this with Heard - https://youtu.be/--Te2eW6viU

Huge Win for Johnny Depp In Court. Amber Faced Multiple Felony Charges - https://youtu.be/gDWbSNcW0aI

ACLU responds, Ambers friends get Subpoenaed - https://youtu.be/Q6eslcu0rzI

The equipment I use:

The video footage was shot using a Canon EOS M50 Mark 2
My microphone is a Blue Yeticaster professional broadcast bundle. With yeti USB microphone, Radius 3 shockmount, and Compass Boom Arm
The lighting I use is a GVM bicolor LED video light
The video editing program I use is Cyberlink Powerdirector 365 version 19
